message.body: Are these plans for you or for both of us?
I meant to hit send like four hours ago.
She didn't say. Would you wanna go?
Oh I don't know. It was probably an invite just for you then.
What did she want to do?

Ok. I've been trying to think of where to have lunch that's quick but I am completely blank. Can you try think too? Even though I don't feel like leaving the house, I know getting out will make me feel better.
Okay. Do you want to do center city or Penn
I was trying to think in center city. But if you can't think of anything there, we can do Penn.
I'm still making myself upset so I literally can't think of anything.
I'm not even hungry now, which is not normal for me.
Do You have a time preference? I don't have any meetings today.
